`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Perfect Software is a myth. Perhaps the key to the right balance is to understand the perceptions of the user and stakeholder."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"The software/products you build are going to be used by a certain set of users or by general users. It is always best to get feedback from the end-users from their user experience. We can release a beta (release candidate) version, roll it out to your stakeholders, other team members, and possibly end-users for feedback."}),`
