`,n.jsxs(e.p,{children:["Same way, when a product solves the fundamental needs of a given problem statement, it can be considered as a ",n.jsx(e.em,{children:"Minimum Viable Product."})]}),`
`,n.jsxs(e.blockquote,{children:[`
