`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Identify the expectation based on the timeline and the resources given. Give the best for programmers, end-users, and future code maintainers. Nothing is always perfect. And most importantly, we need to know when to stop. Do not kill the good program with over-engineering."}),`
